    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《冲突不断》!你将化身为不同的指挥官，穿越森林、火山和沙漠等多种环境，合理运用资源，召集伙伴们，升级科技，击败源源不断的敌人，摧毁敌方防御。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机战局：多样的指挥官与地图提供不同的游戏特性，每一局都是全新的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/10ceff81adc9699c6c5cf96286f409b7.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/10ceff81adc9699c6c5cf96286f409b7.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/42151453844904055c33490a41c14531.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/42151453844904055c33490a41c14531.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兵种与科技升级：选择多样的兵种，使用资源升级随机出现的科技，增强你的战斗力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/fd6dba669bb394b934986be1b49f7c13.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/fd6dba669bb394b934986be1b49f7c13.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/5cd7664ef24b5c738bd49a17953499fa.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/5cd7664ef24b5c738bd49a17953499fa.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能系统：通过宝箱掉落的随机技能，在战场中灵活运用，扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/b191596a431e9177caaf3dd1083f686c.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/b191596a431e9177caaf3dd1083f686c.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品掉落：丰富的物品掉落系统，让你在战斗中获得各种有用的道具，提升战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/55854ff1f1ce5bdf242e91e6e5af5c53.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/55854ff1f1ce5bdf242e91e6e5af5c53.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接挑战了吗？立即加入《冲突不断》，成为最强的指挥官。</p>",
